The paper describes an approach for automatic question answering system using semantic similarity analysis. This involves natural language processing techniques such as part-of-speech tagging and entropy calculation. These techniques are commonly used in the fields of computational linguistics (cs.CL), information retrieval (cs.IR), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), and computational complexity (cs.CC). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper, ordered from most to least likely.
